@GarryColeman
With Handbrake there is a issue of audio getting out of sync toward the end of the movie... (as can be seen on this movie). I found yesterday that Media Coder (http://www.mediacoderhq.com/) does not have that problem.
Generally, for both of them, I would not use video bitrate below 1500 kbps for 720p video(x264), and for audio  below 128 kbps (AAC).
